Package: fusionACS
Title: Integrated, extensive, and high-resolution microdata of U.S.
    households and individuals
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kevin", "Ummel", , "kevin.ummel@yale.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Karthik", "Akkiraju", , "karthik.akkiraju@yale.edu", role = "ctb")
  )
Description: This package provides access to data and tools to facilitate
    otherwise impossible U.S. social survey analyses. A documented
    pseudo-sample of the underlying fusionACS database is made available,
    along with functions to allow efficient microdata assembly and
    analysis. The fusionACS database is the result of statistical fusion
    of social survey microdata to simulate an extensive and
    high-resolution survey of U.S. households and individuals (Ummel et
    al. 2024, Tuccillo et al. 2023).
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://ummel.github.io/fusionACS, https://github.com/ummel/fusionACS
